8, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">55. 判断非空，转换string To int 等方法在工具类</span></p><ol style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 10px !important; padding: 0px !important;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>org.jeecgframework.core.util.oConvertUtils</p></li></ol><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 43px; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(51, 102, 153) !important;\">复制代码</span></p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">56. 给列表单元格加背景色</span></p><ol style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 10px !important; padding: 0px !important;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>&lt;t:dgCol title=&quot;任务类型&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp;field=&quot;type&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; extendParams=&quot;&#39;styler&#39;:fmtype;&quot; query=&quot;true&quot; queryMode=&quot;single&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp;width=&quot;100&quot;&gt;&lt;/t:dgCol&gt;</p></li></ol><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 43px; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(51, 102, 153) !important;\">复制代码</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">extendParams属性添加js方法，然后再调用方法</span></p><ol style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 10px !important; padding: 0px !important;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>function fmtype(val,row,index){<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; var s1 = &#39;background-color: #f89406;;border-radius: 5px;color:#fff;&#39;;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; var s2 = &#39;background-color: #3a87ad;border-radius: 5px;color:#fff&#39;;<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; if (val ==&#39;W&#39;) {<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return s1<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; if (val ==&#39;J&#39;) {<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return s2<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }<br style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p></li><li><p>}</p></li></ol><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-left: 43px; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(51, 102, 153) !important;\">复制代码</span></p><p><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">57. 上传控件不好用问题</span><br style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:16px;word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"color:#000;word-wrap: break-word;\"><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangdaiscott/article/details/28698385\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 102, 153);\">Upload(上传标签)</a></span>采用flesh方式，不同的浏览器对flash支持不同，会出现上传有问题，建议重装flash组件</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '01', '7777', '402881875988e889015988ec36770001');
